extends _layouts/template

block head
  link(rel="stylesheet", href="/css/generic.css")

block content
  .about-container
    header.about-header
      h1.about-title The Shed Place Story
      p.about-subtitle Serving Hohenwald and surrounding communities with quality outdoor structures since 1995

    .about-grid
      .about-image-container
        img.about-image(
          src="/assets/logos/light.svg",
          alt="The Shed Place storefront"
        )
      .about-content
        h2.about-section-title Our Journey
        p.about-text
          | For over 25 years, The Shed Place has been a cornerstone of the Hohenwald
          | community, providing high-quality sheds, trailers, metal buildings, and play
          | sets to families across Tennessee. What started as a small family business
          | has grown into a trusted name in outdoor structures, while maintaining our
          | commitment to personal service and quality craftsmanship.

        p.about-text
          | Under the leadership of Trese Anderson, we've expanded our offerings while
          | staying true to our core values of quality, integrity, and customer satisfaction.
          | We believe in providing not just products, but solutions that enhance our
          | customers' lives and properties.

    .about-values
      .about-value-card
        h3.about-value-title Quality First
        p.about-value-text
          | We partner with top manufacturers and carefully select each product
          | to ensure lasting value for our customers.

      .about-value-card
        h3.about-value-title Customer Focus
        p.about-value-text
          | Our team takes the time to understand your needs and help you find
          | the perfect solution for your space and budget.

      .about-value-card
        h3.about-value-title Local Expertise
        p.about-value-text
          | As members of the Hohenwald community, we understand local needs
          | and provide products suited to our region's conditions.

      .about-value-card
        h3.about-value-title Fair Pricing
        p.about-value-text
          | We believe in transparent, competitive pricing and offering the
          | best value for your investment.

    .about-cta
      p.about-text.mb-6
        | Visit our showroom to see our quality structures in person and speak
        | with our knowledgeable team about your needs.
      a.about-button(href="/contact") Contact Us Today
